        <h1>RPG Design Document</h1>
        <p>
            This RPG game is text-based (supported by minor graphics) RPG game which is played in the browser. 
            The goal of the game is to advance the character with experience, better items, and equipment.
        </p>
        <p>
            The game is single-player, and is player in the browser. Should this be multiplayer?
        </p>

        <section>
            <h2>Character</h2>
            <p>
                A character is defined by his/her attributes and equipment. The combination
                of these two will determine how combate evolves.
            </p>
            <p>
                The characters in the game are highly customizable in the following areas:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Different kind of races</li>
                <li>Both genders: male/female</li>
                <li>All weapons and armor are shown</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Some races also have different skin tones available.</p>

