            <p>Which skills are there? Is the skill a combat skill, magic skill, or a buff?</p>
            <p>
                A skill will do combat or magic damage. This damage is increased by the attributes and equipment.
                This means that if a player is built for combat damage, and uses a magic damage weapon, then this will
                be sub-par to a player that is build for magic damage.
            </p>
            <p>
                A skill has a certain amount of turn cooldown. During this time the skill cannot be used.
            </p>
            <p>
                A magic skill will consume mana. It is important for magic based characters to
                bring mana potions with them.
